text: Ralph Yandell (29 March 1892 - 20 July 1982) was a British gymnast. He competed in the men's team all-around event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1892 births Category:1982 deaths Category:British male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bristol
